data.title: John Wiley & Sons
data.meta_description: kitap_listesi - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document is an inventory list containing 138 items in Turkish. It includes the order number, order ID number, author, book title, volume number, and publisher for each item. The items cover a wide range of topics including architecture, history, medicine, psychology, engineering, and computer science. The list provides basic bibliographic information for planning an acquisition of these materials.
